# Testing conventions

This repo uses Vitest with React Testing Library. When writing or updating tests:

- Query by role and accessible name (getByRole, getByLabelText). Avoid snapshot-only tests and avoid querying by test id unless no accessible query exists.
- Assert observable behavior and accessibility, not implementation details.
- Match existing describe/it naming and the existing test utilities in the package under test.
- Run yarn test for the suite and yarn test:typecheck for types. Run yarn test:update before committing if snapshots are intentionally changed.
- A change is not done until its targeted tests pass locally.
